head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths KEENE, CARL E.

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths KEENE, CARL E.

block.p: KEENE-Carl E., 76 years. Survived by his wife Una and his brother Kenneth. Funeral services today, 2-5, 7-9 PM, at Conway Funeral Home, Northern Boulevard at 83rd and 82nd Streets, Jackson Heights, NY. Funeral Mass Monday, 10:15 AM, at St. Joan of Arc Church, Jackson Heights. Interment at St. Michael's Cemetery, East Elmhurst, NY.
